The paper involves generating natural language from images, which is a task that falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of deep learning techniques and adversarial training suggests that the paper may also fall under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves generating poetry, which is a form of creative writing and may involve some aspects of information retrieval (cs.IR) in terms of finding relevant poetic clues from the image.
